<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ error.code || '500' }} - Error del Servidor | Códigos de Oro</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-negro: #000000;
            --color-oro: #FFD700;
            --color-naranja: #FFA500;
            --color-gris-oscuro: #111111;
            --color-gris-fondo: #1a1a1a;
            --color-rojo: #FF4D4D;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--color-negro);
            color: var(--color-oro);
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, var(--color-gris-oscuro) 0%, var(--color-negro) 100%);
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-oro) 0%, var(--color-rojo) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--color-oro);
        }

        .error-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.7);
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background-color: var(--color-oro);
            color: var(--color-negro);
            border: 2px solid var(--color-oro);
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--color-oro);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--color-oro);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom:hover {
            border-color: var(--color-oro);
            background-color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.05);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--color-rojo);
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        /* Debug info only for local environment */
        .debug-info {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: none; /* Hidden by default */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="warning-icon">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="error-code">{{ error.code || '500' }}</div>
        <h1 class="error-message">Error en la Gala</h1>
        <p class="error-description">
            Parece que algo ha fallado entre bastidores. Nuestros técnicos están revisando la iluminación y el sonido para que todo vuelva a brillar cuanto antes.
        </p>
        
        <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="/" class="btn-custom btn-primary-custom">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
                Volver al inicio
            </a>
            <button onclick="window.location.reload()" class="btn-custom btn-secondary-custom">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right"></i>
                Reintentar
            </button>
        </div>

        @if(app.inDev)
            <div class="debug-info" style="display: block;">
                <strong>Debug Info:</strong>
                <pre>{{ error.stack }}</pre>
            </div>
        @endif
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
